{"tid":1921991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(推上熱門) 警拘 7 人最小 13 歲　指涉「天下制裁」集會襲擊警民關係組警員","createTime":"2020-03-12T09:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T11:19:17.000Z","uid":143355,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1a838b710598bce999005d158c901fbae5a2c67e","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"今年 1 月 19 日民間集會團隊在遮打花園舉行「天下制裁」集會，期間警方指現場出現暴力違法事件，中區警民關係組警員到場要求中止集會，其後受襲。警方今天指經過深入調查，拘捕 7 名涉案人士，他們全部是男性，年齡最小的只有 13 歲，7 人中 6 人為 20 歲以下，警方指有足夠證據顯示被捕人士涉及直接或間接襲擊警務人員，<span style=\"color: red;\">不排除會有更多人被捕</span>。<br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科（行動）警司周旺忠今天指，今年 1 月 19 日遮打花園的集會獲得不反對通知書，但集會期間發生不同的違法及暴力事件，中區警民關係組警員到場要求主辦者終結集會。周旺忠指，警員行動期間遭部份人士「刻意刁難、引起在場人士情緒」，令警員被大批暴徒包圍，拳打腳踢，有警員更被雨傘、伸縮棍及磚頭襲擊，4 名警員受到不同程度傷害。<br />\n<br />\n當日集會申請人劉穎匡，當天傍晚在灣仔遭警方拘捕，警方指劉涉嫌煽動群眾情緒，以及違反不反對通知書條款。<br />\n<br />\n周旺忠指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">調查案件的毒品調查科探員其後翻看大量閉路電視片段，抽絲剝繭，最終鎖定 7 名與案有關人士身份，並在昨天採取拘捕行動。探員在港島半山區、九龍黃大仙及將軍澳等地，以有意圖傷人及非法集結罪，拘捕 7 名男子。他們年齡介乎 13 至 34 歲，報稱的職業為學生、無業及送貨工人等。警員亦在他們的住所，檢取當天犯案時穿著的服飾鞋履等證物。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n指最高刑罰可判囚終身<br />\n<br />\n周旺忠又指，案件仍然調查中，務求將所有人繩之於法。而警方亦關注被捕的 7 名人士中，有 6 人為 20 歲以下。他呼籲青年人切勿以身試法，或以為人多犯法場面犯法會無事。周旺忠指有意圖傷人的最高刑罰，是可處以終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n他又指因為涉案人士犯案時穿上黑衣及幪面，承認警方在調查上有困難。而探員根據犯案人逃跑路線，向沿路線多家商戶及交通機構，要求提供閉路電視片段。被問及有否向巴士公司要求提供片段，周旺忠只稱調查方向廣泛，「牽涉沿路蛛絲馬跡」。<br />\n<br />\n他又重申，探員是經過仔細分析，花費大量時間和精力研究事發經過，「逐吋逐吋、逐點逐點去睇」，強調警方有足夠證據顯示被捕人士涉及直接或間接襲擊警務人員，或者包圍或襲擊警員。<br />\n<br />\n13 歲被捕者准保釋<br />\n<br />\n至於年齡最小的 13 歲被捕者，周旺忠指他因為年紀較細，不宜羈押，所以准許保釋，其餘人士繼續遭扣查，稍後會被落案控告。<br />\n<br />\n周旺忠亦有交代受傷警員情況，他指在事件中，有警員頭部受傷需要縫針；有警員手指骨拆，需要施手術鞏固傷肢；有警員頭骨破裂，需要接受手術，從頭部把磚頭碎片移除，避免傷及腦部，至今仍未康復。<br />\n<br />\n1月19號手足係時候打掃屋企！！！<br />\n清下啲舊衫褲唔係擺係屋企 剪下個柒頭<br />\n心情唔好最好去朋友到住下散下心"},{"pid":"0b617cb090645bf11b7eac1899e7daaae3adf95b","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7db7d0fbe1629dc85d70f3cd0f91dc4e5603ff","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"推推推，救救手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7313a98a3e6e0203e0a435ad4b87af34e1aac1b4","tid":1921991,"uid":114882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"執屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a2ec847dff06a68e17be60be2a74c77ad25eef","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人提提手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fd6132ae87bda542cc0579df2331bb08b4e1e2","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"source：立場新聞"},{"pid":"b0aa88dcee045daea999a8e3d31f0987de80e72b","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77415eaa8271300d69871c8ca98d351b817ead0d","tid":1921991,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc370be4787b1767108071167b384116bc8f41d4","tid":1921991,"uid":198214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"2394e5194fba56fd0eee1b1ab5fc40f7a2091d05","tid":1921991,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"推一推....兩日後唔知幾多個入院....唉..."},{"pid":"ab07ed0d4d95785ea6f7390aa06d0b8ac762c89f","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不排除會有更多人被捕</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n重點啊"},{"pid":"74112c87f4b033a4c1daf8f137e6d4f015456ab4","tid":1921991,"uid":260162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:56:00.000Z","msg":"推ahhhh"},{"pid":"f0b86343d966906f376a0a7493f1574267a448a3","tid":1921991,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"推 執屋"},{"pid":"3d0c3c57da50496d9102c92b0e3aeddffb0a27b0","tid":1921991,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d0a17b216ca4aef59c7bc56d29689f62ea5f31f","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"救救手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08c19b13f217dfccc90296b077dfc658fd52a16","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"成4個鐘都冇人講，推上熱門救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0307148e8cd0e5ebeaddacfd2b69ae6a66b5b937","tid":1921991,"uid":70679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"係咁拉人，但全部都靜係拉搞過狗既人，垃圾小氣狗"},{"pid":"c3d795f510e893543e340dba77aa20f81cce921c","tid":1921991,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea51e4938c0bd3a16394948f6757d7821d1c8bd","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0301c4bc7a3f6b8d993ec0762a1ac6dac5318d","tid":1921991,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"汁屋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce79fbb4acba3b28aa54cedfcf4acd583a6e6a3","tid":1921991,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/454600148528214/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F454600148528214%2F&h=c8b898fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"675913782aa44192c07276d586d85d26bb7a7dbe","tid":1921991,"uid":51266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f154136071dfbe37c06ea42273eb4a86c198c78","tid":1921991,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a838b710598bce999005d158c901fbae5a2c67e","tid":1921991,"uid":143355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"今年 1 月 19 日民間集會團隊在遮打花園舉行「天下制裁」集會，期間警方指現場出現暴力違法事件，中區警民關係組警員到場要求中止集會，其後受襲。警方今天指經過深入調查，拘捕 7 名涉案人士，他們全部是男性，年齡最小的只有 13 歲，7 人中